lign="center" data-vertical-align="top">TI</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">P</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Tidspunkt når meldingen er sendt i UTC<br />(TTMM)</td></tr></tbody></table></article><footer class="footnotes"><article class="footnote" data-name="1" data-unique-footnote-counter="1"><span class="footnoteLabel">1</span> Valgfritt for fartøy underlagt satellittsporing.</article></footer></section></main></body></html>